{"tid":903987,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"田北俊稱23條現立法較好否則2047年可能是國安法","createTime":"2018-11-16T03:43:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-16T04:57:33.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fe898ef754d714c62bd5cc078440f2fc0a0faee1","tid":903987,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T03:43:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1428595_1_20181116103543.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1428595_1_20181116103543.jpg&h=7f632bd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自由黨榮譽主席田北俊認為，若就基本法23條立法，一定會是2003年的「加辣版」，但「加辣」到甚麼情況，中央認為可行，香港人又接受到，是關鍵問題。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，當年提出的23條，不能以言入罪，行為要達到暴力才觸犯法例，處理不到大學生在校園張貼港獨標語的問題，相信再就23條立法，會比當年「辣」。<br />\n<br />\n田北俊說，未來香港對中央的利用價值會越來越小，如果跟北京討價還價，不如現時訂立較好，如果到2047年才立法，到時可能是國安法。<br />\n<br />\n他認為，即使香港無就23條立法，佔中後政府亦採取了不同行政手段，包括取消議員參選資格，以前根本無說明宣誓時速度和口音。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1428595-20181116.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1428595-20181116.htm&d=cVkKFaQom%2Bj3qDTSP7JoTRFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=be9bd7dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1428595-20181116.htm&h=fbfeccd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1428595-20181116.htm</a>"},{"pid":"7e19fe32d13c48f15347bf72ac9a14926d6508f4","tid":903987,"uid":653,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T03:53:14.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家立完23條2047再加國安法都得架啦，反正任鳩佢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"418ceb23127b72241e34ec3c81d6c6287a0e5944","tid":903987,"uid":31841,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T03:55:47.000Z","msg":"2047係唔